    category: "International"
  },
  {
    question: "What types of funds do you advise?",
    answer: "We advise the full spectrum of investment vehicles including UCITS, AIFs, RAIFs, SCSp, and SICAR structures. Our expertise covers private equity, real estate, infrastructure, and hedge fund strategies, with particular strength in carried interest planning.",
