  },
  {
    question: "What is your typical client profile?",
    answer: "Our clients range from high-net-worth individuals with €10M+ in assets to multinational corporations and investment funds managing billions. We particularly excel with clients requiring sophisticated, multi-jurisdictional tax solutions.",
    category: "Clients"
  },
  {
    question: "How quickly can you respond to urgent matters?",
